This paper discusses the construction of transformationally identical and invariant convolutional neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of symmetric operations and input vectors, which are related to artificial intelligence (AI) and neural networks (NE). Finally, the paper mentions the use of a flatten layer, which is related to multimedia (MM).
